full_text: IN THE CIRCUIT COURT OF THE FIFTEENTH JUDICIAL CIRCUIT, IN AND FOR PALM BEACH COUNTY, FLORIDA CRIMINAL DIVISION 05/368 STATE'S ATTORNEY SUBPOENA DUCES TECUM TO: BELLSOUTH TELECOMMUNICATION FAX: 404-378-9289 GREETINGS: --- DUCES TECUM: PLEASE PROVIDE DETAILED CALL RECORDS, TO INCLUDE INCOMING AND OUTGOING FOR THE DATES OF JANUARY 27TH 2005, THROUGH JUNE 24TH 2005, FOR TELEPHONE NUMBER 561-832-4117. YOU MAY COMPLY BY FORWARDING THE REQUESTED INFORMATION TO DETECTIVE MICHELLE D. PAGAN, PALM BEACH POLICE DEPARTMENT, 345 SOUTH COUNTY ROAD, PALM BEACH, FL 33480, TELEPHONE NO. (561) 838-6470, FAX NO. (561) 838-5401. YOU ARE HEREBY COMMANDED TO BE AND APPEAR BEFORE THE STATE'S ATTORNEY or his assistant, in and for Palm Beach County, Florida, at 401 North Dixie Highway, West Palm Beach, Florida for interrogation and the truth to speak, in a certain matter pending and under investigation.
